  ('gate-general-aptitude-quantitative-aptitude-m01', 'gate-general-aptitude-quantitative-aptitude', 'Quantitative Aptitude', '**Quantitative aptitude** rewards speed on percentages, interest, speed-time and averages — reliable GATE aptitude marks.

