  ('gate-general-aptitude-logical-reasoning-series-m01', 'gate-general-aptitude-logical-reasoning-series', 'Logical Reasoning & Series', '**Logical reasoning and series** test pattern recognition and deduction — fast, formula-light GATE aptitude marks.

