  ('gate-core-cs-algorithms-sorting-complexity-m01', 'gate-core-cs-algorithms-sorting-complexity', 'Algorithms: Sorting & Complexity', '**Sorting algorithms** and their analysis are core GATE territory, blending recurrence solving with comparison counting.

