  ('upsc-polity-fundamental-rights-q01', 'upsc-polity-fundamental-rights', 'In which Part of the Constitution are the Fundamental Rights enshrined?', 'Part II (Articles 5–11)', 'Part III (Articles 12–35)', 'Part IV (Articles 36–51)', 'Part IVA (Article 51A)', 'B', 'Fundamental Rights occupy Part III; Part IV holds the Directive Principles and Part IVA the Fundamental Duties.', 0),
