  ('jee-physics-magnetism-emi-q05', 'jee-physics-magnetism-emi', 'A rod of length L moves at speed v perpendicular to a field B. The motional emf is:', 'BL/v', 'BLv', 'Bv/L', 'BLv²', 'B', 'Motional emf is B x L x v for a rod moving perpendicular to the field.', 4),
