  ('jee-physics-optics-q08', 'jee-physics-optics', 'A convex lens of focal length 10 cm forms an image of an object at 20 cm. The image distance is:', '20 cm', '10 cm', '5 cm', '40 cm', 'A', '1/v - 1/u = 1/f gives 1/v = 1/10 - 1/20, so v = 20 cm.', 7),
