  ('ssc-cgl-english-reading-comprehension-q08', 'ssc-cgl-english-reading-comprehension', 'A good first step in RC is to:', 'Skim for the main idea', 'Memorise the passage', 'Read every option first', 'Answer without reading', 'A', 'Skim for the main idea first, then read the questions.', 7),
