  ('ssc-cgl-english-active-passive-voice-q05', 'ssc-cgl-english-active-passive-voice', 'Change to passive: "He will finish the work."', 'The work was finished by him.', 'The work is finished by him.', 'The work will been finished by him.', 'The work will be finished by him.', 'D', 'Future simple passive uses will be + V3.', 4),
