  ('gate-core-cs-digital-logic-q07', 'gate-core-cs-digital-logic', 'A device that selects one of several inputs based on select lines is a:', 'Decoder', 'Multiplexer', 'Flip-flop', 'Counter', 'B', 'A multiplexer routes one selected input to the output based on select lines.', 6),
